{"tid":1494840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京公安飛機帶走港人 譚家翔 先生","createTime":"2019-08-21T20:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T07:02:29.000Z","uid":77165,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"10f2402ed3f5cabfb8ef25b36999c379f9d0c90b","tid":1494840,"uid":77165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T20:17:18.000Z","msg":"21-8-2019<br />\nFlight Ka903 to Beijing<br />\n<br />\n北京公安飛機帶走港人 譚家翔 先生<br />\n2 Beijing polices took away a young man, Mr Tam Ka Cheung, from the plane just landed Beijing!<br />\n<br />\n一手資訊！<br />\n航機抵達後 機艙門打開後ground officer reject 乘客落機 因為要immigration 查核資料。最後結果係要即場做廣播叫乘客approach cabin crew.<br />\n<br />\nFirst hand!<br />\nAfter landing and cabin door opened, the ground officer rejected passenger disembarkation (even crew must be remained on the plane). Because of the immigration officer required to check and cfm once again with the passenger info.<br />\nAfter all, the cabin crew made a public announcement &ldquo; Mr Tam Ka Cheung please kindly approach our cabin crew.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nGround Officer向空服報稱大陸能收到香港警察提供之示威相片或影片，以助內地查核香港示威前線手足。<br />\n<br />\nThe Beijing Ground Officer claimed that the Hk Popo provides front line protestors&rsquo; face photos or videos to Mainland, which is one of the clue for China to commence the inspections and checks!<br />\n<br />\n倘若被拘留 將會與親朋好友失聯<br />\n本人極為擔心該男士安全<br />\n煩請廣傳聯絡其家人好友！<br />\n<br />\nPerhaps, Mr Tam Ka Cheung has been detained, he will lose his connection with his fam and friends! Please help him and forward this!<br />\n<br />\n*譚家翔被帶走前曾向港人表示電話清潔"},{"pid":"5aa21720919d4d1e176e9845e2c6a966581c4cec","tid":1494840,"uid":250580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T20:21:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"43c1cd90be5c6b8939524f850253c6ba6625c518","tid":1494840,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T20:22:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebd3b39d65f7d0c911a110e278677cc63eccbaad","tid"